dlentry.dd:
Inserts a new section / subsection in the document, depending on the current context.
          For example if the current context issect1 then a sect2
          is inserted, and so on;

dd.p:
This action generates and sets unique IDs for:
the element at caret position;
all top-level elements found in the current selection. Additionally, if the selection contains elements from the Docbook ID Options list, they will all receive an unique ID. IDs already set are preserved.
